=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"你買左fast pass先再講啦,<br />\nfast pass有限定你咩時間要去玩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊年6月去左, 買左fast pass 4+cool japan 2,<br />\n大部野都玩左至少一次<br />\n本身極愛好玩刺激野, 但好憎d淨係轉轉下既廢野(如旋轉木馬) <br />\n<br />\n我覺得最正係EVA XR過山車(cool japan期間限定), <br />\n成個feel認真不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有過山車離心力, 個視覺效果又好逼真<br />\n今年好似話重開, 又係期間限定, 有得玩必玩<br />\n<br />\n最唔好玩係minion果個, 轉/chok到個人暈又冇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意minions都係睇巡遊/show就夠<br />\n<br />\n飛天翼龍視角過癮但冇乜離心力,<br />\n感覺都可以, 我玩左2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n荷里活美夢過山車有順向同逆向玩, 同一條軌道<br />\n3架順向車就有1架逆向車, 個座位有得揀音樂順向有單人隊, 逆向就冇但又少d人排<br />\n普通過山車咁lor, 中午至下晝人不多, 我玩左3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\njurassic ride船遊果個會濕身, ok既, 最尾衝落去果d似海洋公園果d但長少少, 激少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係幾乎係得最尾果一下<br />\n<br />\nHarry potter園區d景正, amusement就普通<br />\n玩左禁忌之旅, d 4D有d假, 又轉到我有d暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鷹馬的飛行果日見住佢行行下壞左,<br />\n上左車上左斜既遊客要落番車自己行番落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩左spider man但冇乜印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc580f1231eb9c4b5d081dbd68346c68c01641b5","tid":692234,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e143e629ff2cb55dfae7c76f4fbebecf3991c9","tid":692234,"uid":75354,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"個人覺得哈利波特個butterbeer好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"好甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係真beer+honey可能會正d<br />\n試一次都ok既"},{"pid":"8c0585cf